<div class="r" data-d="0.3" style="margin-top:6px"><span class="lbl lbl-c" style="margin-bottom:14px;display:block">PARTICIPATION RATE &middot; IN-HOUSE VS CADE</span><div class="part-vs"><div class="part-side part-base"><div class="part-tag">Run In-House</div><div class="part-n">~5<span class="part-x">%</span></div><div class="part-l">Industry average participation</div></div><div class="part-vs-mark">vs</div><div class="part-side part-cade"><div class="part-tag">Run With CADE</div><div class="part-n">~39<span class="part-x">%</span></div><div class="part-l">CADE local model average</div><span class="part-mult">Nearly 8x higher</span></div></div></div>

<div class="r" data-d="0.4" style="margin-top:18px"><div class="ffs-stats" style="grid-template-columns:1fr"><div class="ffs-stat"><div class="ffs-n">100<span class="ffs-x" style="font-size:.4em">&nbsp;to&nbsp;</span>400</div><div class="ffs-l">Patient enrollments per provider</div></div></div></div>

<div class="r" data-d="0.42" style="margin-top:30px"><span class="lbl lbl-c" style="margin-bottom:14px;display:block">WHO HANDLES WHAT</span><div class="hw-grid">
<div class="hw-panel hw-cade"><div class="hw-hd"><span class="hw-tag">CADE Runs</span><h4>The entire engine</h4></div><ul class="hw-list"><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Patient enrollment &amp; consent</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Cellular devices shipped to the home</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Clinical monitoring of readings</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Time logging every month</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Audit-ready documentation</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Billing prep &amp; reporting</li></ul></div>
<div class="hw-panel hw-rfmg"><div class="hw-hd"><span class="hw-tag">Your Practice</span><h4>Keeps the upside</h4></div><ul class="hw-list"><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Billed through the practice</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>No financial exposure</li><li><span class="hw-c">&check;</span>Net 60 terms on eligible claims</li></ul></div>
</div></div>

</div></section>

<!-- 08 CADE PRICING -->
<section id="mp-cadeprice" class="sct cbg"><div class="wrap"><div class="r"><span class="num">07</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.08"><span class="lbl lbl-c">CADE PRICING &middot; FEE-FOR-SERVICE</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.14"><h2 class="h2">CMS rates up.<br><span class="ac">A clear margin on every code.</span></h2></div><div class="r" data-d="0.2"><div class="cp-callouts"><div class="cp-call"><div class="cp-call-n">+12<span class="cp-call-x">%</span></div><div class="cp-call-l">CMS allowable increase YoY in 2026 &middot; two new RPM codes added</div></div><div class="cp-call hot"><div class="cp-call-n">$160<span class="cp-call-x" style="font-size:.4em">&nbsp;to&nbsp;</span>300</div><div class="cp-call-l">Typical practice revenue per enrolled patient, per month</div></div></div></div>

<div class="r" data-d="0.26" style="margin-top:8px"><span class="lbl lbl-c" style="margin-bottom:14px;display:block">PER-PATIENT MONTHLY SCENARIOS</span><div class="cp-scen"><div class="cp-scen-row cp-scen-head"><div>Scenario</div><div class="num">Est. Allowable</div><div class="num">CADE Fee</div></div><div class="cp-scen-row"><div class="lab">Avg. RPM Month</div><div class="num">$152</div><div class="num fee">$80</div></div><div class="cp-scen-row"><div class="lab">Avg. CCM Month</div><div class="num">$130</div><div class="num fee">$67</div></div><div class="cp-scen-row"><div class="lab">Avg. RTM Month</div><div class="num">$163</div><div class="num fee">$83</div></div><div class="cp-scen-row"><div class="lab">Avg. PCM Month</div><div class="num">$130</div><div class="num fee">$67</div></div><div class="cp-scen-row cp-scen-total"><div class="lab">Avg. Dual Enrolled (RPM + CCM)</div><div class="num">$282</div><div class="num fee">$147</div></div></div></div>

<div class="r" data-d="0.36" style="margin-top:30px"><span class="lbl lbl-c" style="margin-bottom:14px;display:block">CODE-BY-CODE &middot; 2026 ALLOWABLE VS CADE FEE</span></div>

<div class="r" data-d="0.42" style="margin-top:8px"><div class="cp-grid">

<div class="cp-prog"><div class="cp-prog-h"><div class="cp-prog-code">RPM</div><div class="cp-prog-name">Remote Patient Monitoring</div></div><div class="cp-table"><div class="cp-row cp-head"><div class="cp-c1">CPT</div><div class="cp-c2">Note</div><div class="cp-c4">2026</div><div class="cp-c5">CADE</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99453</div><div class="cp-c2">Initial Setup and Enrollment</div><div class="cp-c4">$20.96</div><div class="cp-c5">$0.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99445</div><div class="cp-c2">RPM and Device Readings (2 to 15 Days)</div><div class="cp-c4">$50.45</div><div class="cp-c5">$26.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99454</div><div class="cp-c2">RPM and Device Readings (16+ Days)</div><div class="cp-c4">$50.45</div><div class="cp-c5">$26.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99470</div><div class="cp-c2">Initial Care Management (10 to 20 Minutes)</div><div class="cp-c4">$25.49</div><div class="cp-c5">$14.75</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99457</div><div class="cp-c2">Initial Care Management (20 Minutes)</div><div class="cp-c4">$50.65</div><div class="cp-c5">$28.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99458</div><div class="cp-c2">Additional Care Management (40 to 60 min)</div><div class="cp-c4">$40.61</div><div class="cp-c5">$21.50</div></div></div></div>

<div class="cp-prog"><div class="cp-prog-h"><div class="cp-prog-code">CCM</div><div class="cp-prog-name">Chronic Care Management</div></div><div class="cp-table"><div class="cp-row cp-head"><div class="cp-c1">CPT</div><div class="cp-c2">Note</div><div class="cp-c4">2026</div><div class="cp-c5">CADE</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99490</div><div class="cp-c2">Initial 20 Minutes</div><div class="cp-c4">$64.85</div><div class="cp-c5">$33.50</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99439</div><div class="cp-c2">Additional Care (20 min)</div><div class="cp-c4">$49.41</div><div class="cp-c5">$26.00</div></div></div></div>

<div class="cp-prog"><div class="cp-prog-h"><div class="cp-prog-code">RTM</div><div class="cp-prog-name">Remote Therapeutic Monitoring</div></div><div class="cp-table"><div class="cp-row cp-head"><div class="cp-c1">CPT</div><div class="cp-c2">Note</div><div class="cp-c4">2026</div><div class="cp-c5">CADE</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">98975</div><div class="cp-c2">Initial Setup and Enrollment</div><div class="cp-c4">$20.96</div><div class="cp-c5">$0.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">98976</div><div class="cp-c2">RTM supply device, respiratory (per 30 days)</div><div class="cp-c4">$50.45</div><div class="cp-c5">$26.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">98977</div><div class="cp-c2">RTM supply device, musculoskeletal (per 30 days)</div><div class="cp-c4">$49.81</div><div class="cp-c5">$26.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">98980</div><div class="cp-c2">RTM treatment mgmt, first 20 min / month</div><div class="cp-c4">$52.96</div><div class="cp-c5">$28.50</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">98981</div><div class="cp-c2">Additional 20 minute monitoring</div><div class="cp-c4">$40.65</div><div class="cp-c5">$22.00</div></div></div></div>

<div class="cp-prog"><div class="cp-prog-h"><div class="cp-prog-code">PCM</div><div class="cp-prog-name">Principal Care Management</div></div><div class="cp-table"><div class="cp-row cp-head"><div class="cp-c1">CPT</div><div class="cp-c2">Note</div><div class="cp-c4">2026</div><div class="cp-c5">CADE</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99424</div><div class="cp-c2">First 30 minutes per calendar month</div><div class="cp-c4">$85.88</div><div class="cp-c5">$44.50</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99425</div><div class="cp-c2">Each additional 30 minutes of PCM, same month</div><div class="cp-c4">$60.32</div><div class="cp-c5">$32.50</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99426</div><div class="cp-c2">PCM by clinical staff directed by physician</div><div class="cp-c4">$66.47</div><div class="cp-c5">$34.00</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99427</div><div class="cp-c2">Each additional 30 min of clinical staff PCM</div><div class="cp-c4">$52.98</div><div class="cp-c5">$28.00</div></div></div></div>

<div class="cp-prog"><div class="cp-prog-h"><div class="cp-prog-code">BHM</div><div class="cp-prog-name">Behavioral Health Management</div></div><div class="cp-table"><div class="cp-row cp-head"><div class="cp-c1">CPT</div><div class="cp-c2">Note</div><div class="cp-c4">2026</div><div class="cp-c5">CADE</div></div><div class="cp-row"><div class="cp-c1">99484</div><div class="cp-c2">Care mgmt svc bhvl hlth cond</div><div class="cp-c4">$58.75</div><div class="cp-c5">$35.00</div></div></div></div>

</div></div>

<div class="r" data-d="0.5"><div class="cp-foot">CADE fees are flat per code. 2026 figures use Medicare national-average allowables. Actual reimbursement varies by region, payer, and patient time.</div></div>

</div></section>

<!-- 09 WHY CADE -->
<section id="mp-whycade" class="sct"><div class="wrap"><div class="r"><span class="num">08</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.08"><span class="lbl lbl-c">WHY CADE</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.14"><h2 class="h2">Effortless. Personal. <span class="ac">Loyal.</span></h2></div><div class="r" data-d="0.18"><div class="wc-lead"><p>This is what we do. We drive this program as a white-labeled extension of your care.</p></div></div><div class="wc-stats" id="mp-stats"></div><div class="wc-diffs" id="mp-diffs"></div>
<div class="team-sec r" data-d="0.5"><span class="lbl lbl-c">YOUR TEAM</span><div class="team-grid" id="mp-team"></div>
<div class="ros-sec"><div class="ros-hd"><h4>Customer Success</h4><div class="line"></div><span class="count">02</span></div><div class="ros-grid cs" id="mp-cs-team"></div></div>
<div class="ros-sec"><div class="ros-hd"><h4>Care Team</h4><div class="line"></div><span class="count">04</span></div><div class="ros-grid ct" id="mp-ct-team"></div></div>
</div></div></section>

<!-- 10 RUN YOUR NUMBERS (calculator) -->
<section id="mp-calc" class="sct"><div class="wrap"><div class="r"><span class="num">09</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.08"><span class="lbl lbl-c">RUN YOUR NUMBERS</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.14"><h2 class="h2">What this could look like<br><span class="ac">for your panel.</span></h2></div>
<div class="r" data-d="0.32"><div class="calc">
<div class="calc-head"><div class="ce">Run Your Numbers</div><h3>What this could look like <span class="ac">for your panel.</span></h3><div class="cd">Move the sliders to model your own panel. Industry-average marks are shown on each. Revenue reflects per-patient-per-month reimbursement, with dual-enrolled patients at the higher end.</div></div>
<div class="calc-grid">
<div class="calc-sliders">
<label class="sl"><div class="sl-top"><span class="sl-lab">Total patients in panel</span><span class="sl-val" id="cv-total">5,000</span></div><div class="sl-track"><input type="range" id="cs-total" min="100" max="30000" step="100" value="5000"></div></label>
<label class="sl"><div class="sl-top"><span class="sl-lab">Eligible insurance patients</span><span class="sl-val" id="cv-elig">40%</span></div><div class="sl-track"><input type="range" id="cs-elig" min="0" max="100" step="1" value="40"><div class="sl-marks"><span class="sl-avg" id="ma-elig">avg 40%</span></div></div></label>
<label class="sl"><div class="sl-top"><span class="sl-lab">Chronic patients</span><span class="sl-val" id="cv-chron">85%</span></div><div class="sl-track"><input type="range" id="cs-chron" min="0" max="100" step="1" value="85"><div class="sl-marks"><span class="sl-avg" id="ma-chron">avg 85%</span></div></div></label>
<label class="sl"><div class="sl-top"><span class="sl-lab">Acceptance rate</span><span class="sl-val" id="cv-acc">50%</span></div><div class="sl-track"><input type="range" id="cs-acc" min="0" max="100" step="1" value="50"><div class="sl-marks"><span class="sl-avg" id="ma-acc">avg 50%</span></div></div></label>
<label class="sl"><div class="sl-top"><span class="sl-lab">Dual enrollment</span><span class="sl-val" id="cv-dual">80%</span></div><div class="sl-track"><input type="range" id="cs-dual" min="0" max="100" step="1" value="80"><div class="sl-marks"><span class="sl-avg" id="ma-dual">avg 80%</span></div></div></label>
</div>
<div class="calc-out">
<div class="co-funnel">
<div class="co-row"><span>Eligible insurance</span><span class="v" id="co-elig">2,000</span></div>
<div class="co-row"><span>Of those, chronic</span><span class="v" id="co-chron">1,700</span></div>
<div class="co-row enr"><span>Enrolled patients</span><span class="v" id="co-enr">850</span></div>
</div>
<div class="co-big"><span class="k">Monthly Revenue</span><span class="num" id="co-mo">$215,560</span><span class="sub">Across all enrolled patients</span></div>
<div class="co-big annual"><span class="k">Annual Projection</span><span class="num" id="co-yr">$2.59M</span><span class="sub">Monthly &times; 12</span></div>
<div class="co-split" id="co-detail">680 dual-enrolled at $297/mo &middot; 170 at $160/mo</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="calc-fine">Modeled estimate for illustration only. Figures are not a guarantee of revenue and depend on enrollment, eligibility, documentation, and final CMS allowables. Per-patient-per-month range reflects stacked program reimbursement; dual-enrolled patients reach the higher end.</div>
</div></div>
</div></section>

<!-- 11 CLOSE -->
<section id="mp-close" class="sct"><div class="wrap"><div class="r"><span class="num">10</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.08"><span class="lbl lbl-c">AT A GLANCE</span></div><div class="r" data-d="0.14"><h2 class="h2"><span class="ac">In one frame.</span></h2></div><div class="r" data-d="0.24"><div class="bento">
<div class="bc w2 accent"><div class="pre">The Whole Idea</div><div class="n">Medicare<span class="x" style="font-size:.32em;color:var(--c)">&nbsp;backed</span></div><div class="s">CMS designed these programs and is pushing providers to use them. The whole model is shifting to proactive, between-visit care.</div></div>
<div class="bc"><div class="pre">Revenue Per Patient</div><div class="n" style="font-size:clamp(34px,4vw,46px);white-space:nowrap">$160<span class="x" style="font-size:.4em">&nbsp;to&nbsp;</span>297</div><div class="l">Per month. Dual-enrolled patients hit the higher end.</div></div>
<div class="bc"><div class="pre">Platform Network</div><div class="n">30K<span class="plus">+</span></div><div class="l">Patients on platform</div></div>
<div class="bc hero"><img src="https://imagedelivery.net/qJvpJU9hpeX3lEcmqZfcwg/ea71bdc8-b2c0-4c20-b8a2-e702a7164900/public" alt="CADE" class="logo"><div class="kw">Connected Care.<br><span class="ac">Built around you.</span></div><div class="tag">Effortless &middot; Personal &middot; Loyal</div></div>
<div class="bc"><div class="pre">2026 Rate Increase</div><div class="n">+12<span class="x">%</span></div><div class="l">CMS allowable, two new RPM codes</div></div>
